{"tid":1278520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我們不是爭取更多 只是守護本來擁有的","createTime":"2019-07-02T12:58:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T13:00:55.000Z","uid":157015,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"aee49dbbaca0785139a17e14c72332e111b10114","tid":1278520,"uid":157015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:58:36.000Z","msg":"許多人以為我們在爭取民主<br />\n但事實係我們只是守護本來擁有的一切<br />\n我們的香港被逐漸蠶食<br />\n<br />\n本來香港引以為傲的制度完善 法治 言論自由<br />\n現在還有嗎 ?<br />\n醫療 教育 房屋 早已被搶奪<br />\n今天 送中惡法 白色恐怖<br />\n本來擁有的都被一一奪去<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">謹記 我們不是在爭取<br />\n而是在守護我們應有的一切<br />\n因為我們從未有機會爭取過更多</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n香港不是原地踏步 而是不斷倒退<br />\n何談進步 何談爭取<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請守護香港</span>"},{"pid":"da2cdc0bd6e6f46fdef11f0419528155ff73f388","tid":1278520,"uid":157015,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:59:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"634ada3863b5829b7f0015eb9b507b1cb7ac97b7","tid":1278520,"uid":157015,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:00:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"315b03f8bfb4d5db6811f52be763fc6dd1e014a9","tid":1278520,"uid":157015,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:00:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c495d8d85a0dd856c05cd160f8f2ca98b77ebae","tid":1278520,"uid":157015,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:00:55.000Z","msg":"推"}]}